data.description: Welcome to your thoughtfully upgraded home in the The Estates of Valley Ranch, a small pocket of the highly sought after San Antonio neighborhood. This immaculately-kept home has been upgraded with energy efficiency in mind. Solar panels, solar screens on the double-paned windows, whole house air filter, high-end HVAC units and a water softener are among some of the upgrades in the home. In addition to the sprawling and bright open floor plan with plenty of space for everyone, there's a dedicated home office on the first floor, theater room upstairs, not one but TWO large living spaces, tons of storage throughout and a massive 3-car garage. Venturing out, the neighborhood has two large pools, a playground, tennis courts, gym, basketball court and walking trails. Shopping, restaurants, Government Canyon State Nature Area and entertainment are all close by. No city taxes and Northside ISD. Schedule your showing today!
